### 11.4 Prediction Function
A prediction function was created to classify new product reviews as either human-written or AI-generated. The function applies the same preprocessing and TF-IDF transformation used during training before generating a prediction with the trained Linear SVM model.

def predict_review(review):
    """
    Predict whether a review is human-written or AI-generated.
    """
    cleaned_review = clean_text(review)
    review_tfidf = tfidf.transform([cleaned_review])
    prediction = best_model.predict(review_tfidf)[0]

    if prediction == 1:
        return "AI-generated / Computer-generated review"
    else:
        return "Human-written / Original review"
