## 12. Advanced Model: DistilBERT Transformer

### 12.1 Introduction to DistilBERT
To extend the project beyond traditional machine learning, a DistilBERT was trained as an advanced transformer-based model using the same train-test split as the traditional models. Unlike TF-IDF, it learns contextual language representations from the original review text.

